* {{topt|I just want to help them, I think they need help.}}
** '''Player:''' I just want to help them, I think they need help.
** '''Cyreg Paddlehorn:''' Aye, everyone in these lands needs help. I'm sorry though, it's just not safe and it's not likely to get safer any time soon.
** '''Cyreg Paddlehorn:''' Look, I feel for them, I really do. They're fighting the good fight out there and unfortunately, some of them probably won't live through it.
** '''Cyreg Paddlehorn:''' Ivan in particular I feel sorry for. He's the youngest of their group and he's seen too few winters to be involved in such toil.
** '''Player:''' Then tell me how to find them. I can help them.
** '''Cyreg Paddlehorn:''' I support their cause. That doesn't mean I want to die for them though. I'm sorry, but I will not risk the wrath of the vampyres.
